  </exercise>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp27795280" class="critical-thinking">
  <title>Critical Thinking Question</title>
  <exercise id="fs-idp26454480">
    <problem id="fs-idp52049488">
      <para id="fs-idp100424976">Should people typically pay more attention to their real income or their nominal income? If you choose the latter, why would that make sense in today’s world? Would your answer be the same for the 1970s?</para>
    </problem>
  </exercise>
</section>
